stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> LapStart
    LapStart --> Killed: kill switch tripped
    LapStart --> BoundTrip: max_iterations / max_tokens / max_wallclock_s exceeded
    LapStart --> RunAgent: no trip
    RunAgent --> GateCheck: runner returns RunResult
    GateCheck --> Done: verdict.passed AND stop_condition_met AND (no approval needed OR approved)
    GateCheck --> Pause: verdict.passed AND stop_condition_met AND approval required but not granted
    GateCheck --> Stall: verdict failed AND no_progress_window laps unchanged
    GateCheck --> Continue: verdict failed, still making progress
    Continue --> LapStart: next lap
    Killed --> [*]: Outcome(KILLED)
    BoundTrip --> [*]: Outcome(HALT, reason)
    Done --> [*]: Outcome(DONE, "gate-passed")
    Pause --> [*]: Outcome(PAUSE, "awaiting-approval")
    Stall --> [*]: Outcome(HALT, "no progress in last N laps")
